-- IndusInd Bank to Raise 10 Billion Rupees This Year, Economic Times Reports
-- Rakteem Katakey
-- 2010-06-29T01:46:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/indusind-bank-to-raise-10-billion-rupees-this-year-economic-times-reports.html

          
          
             IndusInd Bank Ltd. will raise 10
billion rupees ($216 million) by selling shares this financial
year, the Economic Times reported, citing two people familiar
with the matter. The money may be raised by selling shares to
institutions or by issue of global depository receipts,
according to the report.  
